snippet.title: AEW: Fight Forever | Giant Swing in the Ring Trailer
snippet.description:
He hears the whispers, he sees the writing… 25% of the Black Pool Combat Club and former ROH champion of the world Claudio Castagnoli makes his Giant Swing in the Ring debut in AEW: Fight Forever.

The Season Pass 3 Content Breakdown:
 - Swerve Strickland
 - Claudio Castagnoli
 - Jamie Hayter
 - Day and Evening Beach Maps
 - 33 brand new moves
 - 42 new skin and attire options
 - 11 all new music tracks
